<h2>Changes</h2>
<ul>

<li>Redirecting Chat to Messages now also changes the nav link text on desktop</li>
<li>Renamed the Hide Messages drawer option to Hide Chat drawer</li>
<li>Fixed back navigation after using a restored Retweets/Likes link under a focused Tweet</li>
<li>Fixed the Messages nav item icon not being active after redirecting Chat to Messages</li>
</ul>
